### Partner Integration - HTTP Samples

### Get All Books
GET https://localhost:5001/api/books
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Available Books
GET https://localhost:5001/api/books/available
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Categories
GET https://localhost:5001/api/bookcategories
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a Book
POST https://localhost:5001/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Domain-Driven Design",
  "author": "Eric Evans",
  "isbn": "978-0321125217",
  "publishedYear": 2003,
  "isAvailable": true,
  "bookCategoryId": null
}

###

### Update a Book
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Domain-Driven Design (Updated)",
  "author": "Eric Evans",
  "isbn": "978-0321125217",
  "publishedYear": 2003,
  "isAvailable": false,
  "bookCategoryId": null
}

###

### Delete a Book
DELETE https://localhost:5001/api/books/{{bookId}}

###
